{"title":"Hello World","date":"2021-05-20T10:06:35.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 20, 2021","L":"05/20/2021","MM-DD":"05-20"},"link":"hello-world.html","tags":["front-end","hexo"],"categories":["Other"],"updated":"2021-06-12T13:36:20.765Z","content":"<h2 id=\"new-blog\">New Blog<a title=\"#new-blog\" href=\"#new-blog\"></a></h2>\n<p>由于之前的博客 hexo 和主题版本过老，不便升级；设置了众多花里胡哨的功能且没有做配置记录，难以维护；长期咕咕咕不更新 blog，没有价值，故今日重置。</p>\n<p>目前 blog 基于 hexo，主题使用 Inside，灵感来自 <a href=\"https://b.earthc.moe/\" target=\"_blank\">Ear7hc</a>。主要风格保持简洁美观。博客内容主要记录学习笔记等技术文章，可能会有随笔、读书笔记等文学类文章。技术类文章的书写规范参考自<a href=\"https://github.com/ruanyf/document-style-guide\" target=\"_blank\">中文技术文档的写作规范</a>和<a href=\"https://github.com/sparanoid/chinese-copywriting-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\">中文文案排版指北</a>。</p>\n<p><strong>What’s past is prologue.</strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"configuration-record\">Configuration Record<a title=\"#configuration-record\" href=\"#configuration-record\"></a></h2>\n<p>在这里记录对 Blog 所做的各项配置，便于后期维护，持续更新。</p>\n<h3 id=\"文章自定义-url\">文章自定义 URL<a title=\"#文章自定义-url\" href=\"#文章自定义-url\"></a></h3>\n<p>hexo 默认的文章 URL 为时间 + 标题的格式，不仅不利于 seo，本身也不美观，所以选择自定义：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>修改 hexo 配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 <code>permalink</code> 为 <code>:urlname.html/</code>，最后的 / 是必要的。</li>\n<li>方便起见，修改 post 模板文件 <code>scaffolds/post.md</code>，在 Front-Matter 中添加 <code>urlname</code> 字段，通过该字段自定义文章的 URL。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"代码块复制功能\">代码块复制功能<a title=\"#代码块复制功能\" href=\"#代码块复制功能\"></a></h3>\n<p>参考自<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/2020/hexo-theme-inside-plugin\" target=\"_blank\">【持续更新】Hexo + inside 博客个性化定制</a>，利用 Inside 主题的注入功能，修改主题配置文件 <code>_config.inside.yml</code>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">plugins:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># 全局加载 Font Awesome 的 CSS</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># 插入依赖 libs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/clipboard@2.0.4/dist/clipboard.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fiteen/fiteen.github.io@v0.1.0/clipboard-use.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fiteen/fiteen.github.io@v0.1.1/clipboard.css</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># inside 主题没有引入 jQuery 框架，需要手动引入</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">//cdnjs.loli.net/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># 插件生效范围：post 和 page</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"attr\">position:</span> [<span class=\"string\">post</span>, <span class=\"string\">page</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">template:</span> <span class=\"string\">|</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">      &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/clipboard@2.0.4/dist/clipboard.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">      &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fiteen/fiteen.github.io@v0.1.0/clipboard-use.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">      &lt;link href=&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fiteen/fiteen.github.io@v0.1.1/clipboard.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>复制按钮的样式对深色主题不很友好，缺乏前端知识暂时不便更改，有需要的可自行更改。</p>\n<h3 id=\"配置头像和站点图标\">配置头像和站点图标<a title=\"#配置头像和站点图标\" href=\"#配置头像和站点图标\"></a></h3>\n<p>主题默认配置了使用 <em>gravatar</em> 获取邮箱对应头像，但无代理时 <em>gravatar</em> 似乎不能正常加载头像，所以将头像和站点图标一并放置到 <code>source</code> 目录下，修改主题配置文件 <code>_config.inside.yml</code>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Sidebar profile</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">profile:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\"># You can set Avatar URL directly</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">avatar:</span> <span class=\"string\">avatar.jpg</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># ···</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Favicon, default to `favicon.ico`</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">favicon:</span> <span class=\"string\">favicon.ico</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"自定义-404-页面\">自定义 404 页面<a title=\"#自定义-404-页面\" href=\"#自定义-404-页面\"></a></h3>\n<p>Inside 主题自带有 404 页面，但是当从外部直接访问不存在的站点链接时仍然会显示 GitHub Pages 原生的 404 页面，很不美观，查阅资料后发现在根目录下放置有 <code>404.md</code> 或 <code>404.html</code> 时，GitHub Pages 会跳转该 404 页面。鉴于以下原因：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Inside 主题的 404 页面是每次重新生成的，不便于把该 html 直接拷贝到根目录。</li>\n<li>hexo 会渲染 <code>source</code> 目录下的 md 文件和 html 文件，且不清楚是否因为和主题的 404 文件冲突，<code>source/404.html</code> 不会被拷贝到 <code>public</code> 目录下。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>按如下配置：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>将 404 页面设置为跳转 Inside 自带的 404 页面，<code>source/404.html</code>（url 中 404 之后的 / 依旧是必要的）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class=\"meta-keyword\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span>404<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">http-equiv</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;refresh&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">content</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;0; url=https://ninecr.tk/404/&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改 hexo 配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Directory</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">skip_render:</span> [<span class=\"string\">README.md</span>, <span class=\"number\">404.</span><span class=\"string\">html</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>enjoy it!</p>\n<h3 id=\"夜间模式\">夜间模式<a title=\"#夜间模式\" href=\"#夜间模式\"></a></h3>\n<ul class=\"φbs\">\n<li><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\"><i></i>待完成</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Waiting for upgrading~</strong></p>\n","prev":{"title":"近来所思","link":"what-I-want.html"},"plink":"https://ninecr.tk/hello-world.html/","toc":[{"id":"new-blog","title":"New Blog","index":"1"},{"id":"configuration-record","title":"Configuration Record","index":"2","children":[{"id":"文章自定义-url","title":"文章自定义 URL","index":"2.1"},{"id":"代码块复制功能","title":"代码块复制功能","index":"2.2"},{"id":"配置头像和站点图标","title":"配置头像和站点图标","index":"2.3"},{"id":"自定义-404-页面","title":"自定义 404 页面","index":"2.4"},{"id":"夜间模式","title":"夜间模式","index":"2.5"}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"https://ninecr.tk/hello-world.html/\" title=\"Hello World\">https://ninecr.tk/hello-world.html/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a>)"}}